{"tid":215231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元秋又提創新建議    倡訓練流浪貓捉老鼠","createTime":"2017-04-24T09:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T16:11:56.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd5358ed1a4ebe62bdfab90e3e638e9221a439a","tid":215231,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170424/large/1493025942_71f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170424%2Flarge%2F1493025942_71f0.jpg&h=6b0d535e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會今召開研究動物權益相關事宜小組委員會會議，商討政府處理流浪動物方面的工作。漁護署在2015年1月接納愛護動物協會及保護遺棄動物協會建議，在長洲及元朗大棠試驗為期3年的「捕捉、絕育、放回」（TNR）計劃，為捕獲的流浪狗絕育，再放回原居地，以新方式控制流浪狗數目。計劃推行至今2年，署方指現階段作出結論為時尚早，認為仍有待取得更多數據，方可進一步評估計劃的成效。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯陳克勤及民主黨鄺俊宇提問，政府會否計劃擴大試驗試劃，於更多地區實施。食衛局副局長陳肇始回應指，對此局方持開放態度，並認為要先累積實驗計劃的經驗，進一步評估計劃，亦需要與各區進行溝通。<br />\n公民黨譚文豪提出，政府是否考慮開放動物中心，讓市民可於中心內直接領養動物。漁護署助理署長薛漢宗稱，領養中心需另尋覓地方及增加人手作處理，需要時間作長遠計劃。<br />\n<br />\n當局回應小組主席蔣麗芸時指，去年一共捕捉及接收約800隻流浪猫。蔣麗芸隨即表示，「有冇考慮訓練吓啲流浪貓捉老鼠呀？」她笑言捕捉老鼠為猫之天性，「可以諗諗去訓練佢哋！」"},{"pid":"a240d0593e10c31bd87c3c6735eacf316ec7304f","tid":215231,"uid":38351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:01:33.000Z","msg":"講野唔經大腦，佢算違反天性嗎？"},{"pid":"7b03e55968f42fd1e259d9d932090d29d0443337","tid":215231,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"班生番"},{"pid":"a523fc0b560910458acffc68fb50cce6cc8991cd","tid":215231,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"鼠王芬後繼有人，鼠王秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3513e2f09e5cadbf5e81f9c07be7ee46ef0ce76c","tid":215231,"uid":23957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼠王芬後繼有人，鼠王秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家係貓王秋，鼠王芬喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae041194946b6b1d3971151fc71326d6a9a065b","tid":215231,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:10:27.000Z","msg":"之後再訓練流浪狗捉流浪貓"},{"pid":"ae816435814c0eacb07b08f134a68b97edb2d0c6","tid":215231,"uid":3212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:11:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之後再訓練流浪狗捉流浪貓</blockquote><br />\n再訓練流浪漢捉流浪狗"},{"pid":"1376704e55bbafb8aa5d149df23163d33c042411","tid":215231,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之後再訓練流浪狗捉流浪貓</blockquote><br />\n再訓練流浪漢捉流浪狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再訓練食環處捉流浪漢"},{"pid":"b24894bc8c0f6e48c9db1fef7c27a98ac3249d39","tid":215231,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"應該訓練流浪貓抄完垃圾桶，執返好佢"},{"pid":"04a1838d856a146eee2a4c867f11e7748401928d","tid":215231,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"訓練下你個屄腦好撚過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b2dedfd33371a90da680f0813ce7f52abbcec9","tid":215231,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之後再訓練流浪狗捉流浪貓</blockquote><br />\n再訓練流浪漢捉流浪狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再訓練食環處捉流浪漢</blockquote><br />\n再訓練老鼠捉食環"},{"pid":"2873b94fce1f3b438401903f597b6d589b04dd67","tid":215231,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之後再訓練流浪狗捉流浪貓</blockquote><br />\n再訓練流浪漢捉流浪狗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再訓練食環處捉流浪漢</blockquote><br />\n再訓練老鼠捉食環</blockquote><br />\n鬥獸棋咩屌"},{"pid":"434c91770562abdc3e99b481af0b46878e3efd31","tid":215231,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:11